§0content and carefree§0
§0to a fault. To their§0
§0doom.§0
§0
§0  Darkness crept in,§0
§0unnoticed.§0
§0
§0
§4          ·ï¡÷¡ï·§0

#- §4          ·ï¡÷¡ï·§0
§0
§0  Sensing a weakness§0
§0in the people, it mani-§0
